/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-chuvstva field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-inline clearfix&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Чувства:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/chuvstvo/vdohnovenie&quot;&gt;Вдохновение&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item odd&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/chuvstvo/pokoy&quot;&gt;Покой&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/chuvstvo/svoboda&quot;&gt;Свобода&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-fotosource field-type-link-field field-label-inline clearfix&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Источник фото:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://wallhere.com/en/wallpaper/677459&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;https://wallhere.com/en/wallpaper/677459&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
